* Edit sr.sh, and change all the locations where you see "sadek"
** gitbasedir should be the git base directory (not inside the git repo directory, but its parent directory)
** webbasedir should be your web root
** you can change all the defaults for the script

* Edit config_si.php and replace all the strings with brackets "<BLAHBLAH>"
* put config_si.php in your git base directory

run "./sr.sh -h" for help
